<title>UK: Cowie welcomes MMC clearance for bus merger.</title>
<headline>Cowie welcomes MMC clearance for bus merger.</headline>
<dateline>LONDON 1997-03-18</dateline>
<text>
<p>Cowie Group Plc on Tuesday welcomed the UK Monopolies and Merger Commission's (MMC) clearance of its merger with British Bus Group Ltd.</p>
<p>The agreed 282 million stg acquisition by Cowie, the UK leasing-to-bus group, is the largest so far in the UK bus industry.</p>
<p>-- London newsroom +44 171 542 4020</p>
